name: Voxel Dreams: K-Food Series #02: DJ Beer 디스크 자키 맥주 (diseukeu jaki maegju), by The Chef
description: This is DJ, The Philosophers bistro's signature beer, a dry lager, with a roasted malt bost, and mineral water from Mount Kulun. This is The Chef's version of the Korean watery beer Snoopy, Psy and him tried in Gangnam. The glass is blown by The Alchemist.
